TY  - JOUR
T1  - Comments on the Two-Product, Single-Machine, Static Demand, Infinite Horizon Lot Scheduling Problem
AU  - Shaoxiang, Chen
Y1  - 1993/03/01
PY  - 1993
DA  - 1993/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.39.3.387
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.39.3.387
